title: Trish Stratus
summary: Patricia Anne Stratigeas (/ˈstrætɪdʒiəs/; born December 18, 1975) better known by the ring name Trish Stratus, is a Canadian fitness master, fitness model and professional wrestler. Often regarded as one of the greatest women's performers, she was also one of the most popular female superstars in World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE).[9][10]
